{
    "name": "Ratfolk Tinkerer",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Before Combat</b> If he can, the tinkerer sets an ambush in an area with multiple entrances and exits.<br/><b>During Combat</b> The tinkerer shares his space with allies to make sneak attacks. If he needs to escape, the tinkerer uses his <i>potion of pass without trace</i>."
        },
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> warm deserts or urban"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Ratfolk are adept at finding and disarming traps, which they scavenge to add to their warrens\u2019 defenses."
        }
    ],
